Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,數個世紀來  聖殿騎士團\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For centuries, the Order of the Knights Templar...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在尋找傳說中的伊甸蘋果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}have searched for the mythical Apple of Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們相信其中蘊含的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They believe it contains not only
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.47,0:00:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅是人類第一次違抗命令的種子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the seeds of man's first disobedience,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是打開自由意志的鑰匙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but the key to the free will itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要找到遺寶  破解它的秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If they find the relic and decode its secrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們就將擁有控制所有自由思想的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they will have the power to control all freedom of thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺客兄弟會  是他們唯一的阻礙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Only the brotherhood called the Assassins stands in their way...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,153.21)}{\fn方正宋黑_GBK\fs11\b0\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\fad(1000,900)}西班牙  安達盧西亞  1492年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.33,0:01:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗教裁判所終於將西班牙交給了聖殿騎士團\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Inquisition has finally delivered Spain to the Templars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穆罕默德蘇丹和他的人還在格拉納達負隅頑抗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sultan Muhammad and his people still hold out in Granada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果能抓住他的兒子  他的小王子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But if his son, the prince, is captured,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.59,0:02:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他必將獻出城池  還有伊甸蘋果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he will surrender the city and the Apple of Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  阿圭拉·德·納哈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you, Aguilar de Nerha,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.97,0:02:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否起誓在自由之戰中守護我們的刺客兄弟會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}swear to honor our order in the fight for freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了人類抵抗聖殿騎士團的暴政\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To defend mankind against Templars' tyranny,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守護自由意志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and preserve free will?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我起誓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果伊甸蘋果落入他們之手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If the Apple falls into their hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.07,0:02:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖殿騎士團將毀滅一切阻礙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the Templars will destroy everything that stands in their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抗議  反對  自由思考是我們的權利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Protest, dissent, our right to think for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向我起誓  哪怕犧牲你自己的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Swear to me that you will sacrifice your life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至這裏所有人的性命  也不會令其落入他們之手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and lives of everyone here to keep it from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命  師父\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, Mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的生命不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our lives are nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊甸蘋果才是一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Apple is everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雄鷹之靈  將守護我們的未來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The spirit of the Eagle, will watch over the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都盲目追尋著真相時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where other men blindly follow the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謹記  一切皆虛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}remember, nothing is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都被道德或法律束縛時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where other men are limited by morality or law,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謹記  無事不允\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}remember, everything is permitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在黑暗中侍奉光明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We work in the darkness to serve the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們  是刺客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We are Assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}刺客信條
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,213.21)}{\fn方正宋黑_GBK\fs11\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\fad(1000,900)\c&HBCEDFE&}墨西哥  下加州  1986年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的生命不是你個人的  卡爾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your blood is not your own, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們找到我們了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They've found us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要活在暗處\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Live in the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走  快走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go! Go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,217.229)}{\fn方正宋黑_GBK\fs11\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\fad(0,700)\c&HFFFFFF&}30年後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,213.21)}{\fn方正宋黑_GBK\fs11\b0\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\fad(1000,900)\c&HD0F3FF&}美國德州  亨茨維爾監獄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是來拯救我的靈魂的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're here to save my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我瞭解到今天是你生日\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I understand it is your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日派對正要開始呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The party is just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下  你讓我緊張\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sit down. You're making me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主啊  洗刷我的罪孽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lord, wash away my sin,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我將重新潔淨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I will be clean, once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不怎麼信《聖經》  是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're not much for the Bible, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡勒姆·林奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Be it known that Callum Lynch
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被判謀殺罪  將於今日\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}has been found guilty of capital murder
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即2016年10月21日  執行死刑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and sentenced to die on this day, October 21st 2016.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囚犯有什麼遺言嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Does the prisoner wish to make a final statement?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請轉告我父親  就說我們地獄再見\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell my father that I'll see him in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫索菲婭·萊肯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My name is Dr. Sophia Rikkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚6點整  你被執行死刑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}At 6 P.M. yesterday evening, you were executed
