Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別碰他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't touch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊  勇敢去做啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go ahead. Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這裏不是囚犯  卡爾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are not a prisoner here, Cal.
