Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機械臂準備完畢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Arms ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  卡爾  我也不喜歡用這種方式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry, Cal, this is not the way I like to do things.
