Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想從我身上得到什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的過去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認真聽我說  卡爾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Listen to me carefully, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你即將進入阿尼姆斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're about to enter the Animus.
