Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:22:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人都不知道  沒人知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nobody else knew. Nobody.
