Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.45,0:29:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1492年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}1492.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.21,0:30:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰爭  宗教迫害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}War, religious prosecution,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.08,0:30:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是托爾克馬達法官及騎士團成員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the closest Father Torquemada or any of our Order
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.93,0:30:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尋找伊甸蘋果最接近成功的一次了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}came to a finding the Apple of Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.12,0:30:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還好嗎  朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How are you, my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.59,0:30:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.73,0:30:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.41,0:30:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周  等長老們會面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Next week when the Elders meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.95,0:30:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會就是否中斷你的阿布斯泰戈項目進行投票\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we shall vote to discontinue your Abstergo project.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.18,0:30:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們覺得  每年給你的三十億資金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We feel that giving you 3 billion annually,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.98,0:30:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花在別處會有更大的用途\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}could be better spent elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.10,0:30:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三十億相比...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tri billion is nothing compared to...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.69,0:30:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們勝利了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.94,0:30:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們已經不在乎他們的公民自由了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People are no longer care about their civil liberties,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.26,0:30:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們只在乎自己的生活水平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they care about their standard of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.93,0:30:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現代世界已經拋棄自由這種理念了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The modern world has outgrown notions like freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.36,0:30:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們樂於盲從\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They are content to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.45,0:30:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要自由意志尚存  威脅就依然存在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The threat remains while free will exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.77,0:30:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,數個世紀以來  我們試圖通過宗教\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For centuries we try with religion,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.23,0:30:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政治  以及現在的消費主義  來剷除異議\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with politics and now consumerism to eliminate dissent.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.83,0:30:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在難道不是時候嘗試科學辦法了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Isn't it the time we gave a science a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.96,0:30:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我女兒比我們所有人都要更接近成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My daughter is closer than we've ever been.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.80,0:31:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你美麗的女兒怎麼樣了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How is your beautiful daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.59,0:31:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她追蹤到了伊甸蘋果的守護者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She has traced protectors of the Apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.39,0:31:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪兒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.48,0:31:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安達盧西亞  1492年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Andalucia, 1492.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.10,0:31:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的後人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The descendents?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.98,0:31:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的後人都死光了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All the blood lines have died out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.86,0:31:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下一個\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.40,0:31:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們追蹤他的血脈到500年前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We've traced his back 500 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.92,0:31:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,定位到刺客兄弟會身上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to the Assassin's Brotherhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.48,0:32:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻覺  就是我們所謂的"血緣效應"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hallucinations are what we call the "Bleeding effect."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.61,0:32:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回溯後的畫面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Images of your regression,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.20,0:32:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潛藏在你現在的視界裏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}laying themselves over your present day field of vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.45,0:32:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你允許的話  我可以教你怎麼控制它們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you allow me, I can teach you how to control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.13,0:33:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退下  我可以搞定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stand down. I have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.33,0:33:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨她去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let her be.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.04,0:33:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那台機器  到底是什麼東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What is it? The machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.54,0:33:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是基因記憶機器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's genetic memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.54,0:33:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過使用阿尼姆斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}By using the Animus,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.42,0:33:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可以獲取祖先的記憶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we can relive lives of those who made us who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.94,0:33:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到的情形  感覺很真實\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What I saw in there, it felt real.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.42,0:33:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.95,0:33:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在某種程度上是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.83,0:33:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別跟我耍花招\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.74,0:33:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在感覺不一樣了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I feel different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.08,0:33:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼有攻擊性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why the aggression?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.54,0:33:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本就是個有攻擊性的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm an aggressive person.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.30,0:33:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼監獄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What kind of prison is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.76,0:33:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏不是監獄  卡爾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not a prison, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.84,0:33:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你乖乖合作  就會瞭解到更多東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'll learn more if you cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.10,0:33:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.65,0:34:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我餓了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.36,0:34:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.68,0:34:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}林奇\N1979年-現在
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.14,0:34:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}對卡勒姆·林奇的擔憂加深
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.14,0:34:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}黑幫突襲當地辦事處\N林奇必死無疑
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.67,0:34:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.98,0:34:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道關於你的一切  卡爾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know everything about you, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.11,0:34:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的醫療數據  你的心理檔案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your medical data, your psychological profile,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.31,0:34:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及你MAO-A基因的變異\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the mutations in your MAO-A gene.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.20,0:35:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你在寄養家庭的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know about the foster homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.95,0:35:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在少管所的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The juvenile homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.12,0:35:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是遺傳和犯罪存在關聯的活生生的證據\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are a living proof of the link between heredity and crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.33,0:35:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是怎麼找到我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How did you find me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.38,0:35:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們先找到了阿圭拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We found Aguilar.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.92,0:35:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被逮捕時  你的DNA被發現與他的相匹配\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When you were arrested, your DNA matched his.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.18,0:35:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-阿圭拉是誰  -你的祖先\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Who is Aguilar? - Your ancestor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.31,0:35:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的家族祖上都是刺客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}His family were Assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.18,0:35:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們被聖殿騎士團  托爾克馬達  和你看到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They were burnt at the stake by the Templars,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.06,0:35:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個黑衣騎士奧哈達綁在柱子上燒死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Torquemada and the black knight you saw, Ojeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.61,0:35:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿圭拉繼承了刺客大業\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Aguilar took up the Assassins' cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.71,0:35:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你經常外出嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you go out much?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.95,0:35:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比你外出的時候多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}More than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.20,0:35:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏的其他人呢  也都是實驗室裏的小白鼠嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And the others in here? Are they the lab rats too?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.70,0:35:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們也是刺客  跟他們的祖先一樣都是殺手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They are Assassins, murderers like their ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.00,0:35:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你一樣  卡爾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like you, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.17,0:35:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天生就具有暴力傾向\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All born with predisposition to violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.31,0:36:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.85,0:36:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你殺了那個人  -他是個皮條客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You killed the man. - A pimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.40,0:36:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會再次殺人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Would you kill again?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.49,0:36:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸福的一家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Happy families.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.49,0:36:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一定為你感到很驕傲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She must be very proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.16,0:36:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.66,0:36:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她被一名刺客殺死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She was killed by an Assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.33,0:36:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你母親的遭遇一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.55,0:36:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.68,0:36:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父親殺了我母親\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My old man killed my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.64,0:36:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那讓你是什麼感覺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And how does that make you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.27,0:36:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想殺了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.52,0:36:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要麼我們讓這事影響我們一輩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Either we let it to effect us for the rest of our lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.40,0:37:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要麼採取點措施\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or we just do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.20,0:37:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你選擇了暴力  我選擇了科學\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You turn to violence, I turn to science.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.99,0:37:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是伊甸蘋果  卡爾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's the Apple of Eden, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.62,0:37:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信它真的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I believe it exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.54,0:37:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《聖經》告訴我們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Bible tells us
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.52,0:37:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中蘊含了人類第一次違抗命令的種子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it contained the seed of man's first disobedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.80,0:37:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也有些人認為\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But there are those of us who believe that
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.06,0:37:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝  或某種古文明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}God or some ancient civilization
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.43,0:37:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我們留下了一張指示圖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}have left us a road map
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.72,0:37:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫助我們瞭解人為什麼會有暴力性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to understand why people are violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.02,0:37:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據稱伊甸蘋果最後一次出現是在阿圭拉手上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Aguilar was the last person known to have had it in his possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.65,0:37:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要你查出他把那東西藏在哪兒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need you to find out where he hid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.24,0:37:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為我是來接受治療的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought I was here to be cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.30,0:37:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴力就是一種疾病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Violence is a disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.49,0:37:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟癌癥一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.37,0:37:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且如同癌癥  我們希望有一天能控制住它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And like cancer, we hope to control it one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.58,0:37:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是暴力讓我活到了今天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Violence is what kept me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.38,0:37:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚴格來說  你已經死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well technically, you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.42,0:38:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我餓了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.34,0:38:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能得到什麼好處\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's in it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.55,0:38:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦我的研究完成了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Once my research is complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.09,0:38:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就沒必要把你關在這裏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}there is no reason to keep you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.02,0:38:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能過上以前的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I get my life back?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.35,0:38:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更好  你能擁有全新的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Better. A new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.19,0:38:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是餓了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.55,0:38:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道他是什麼人  也不清楚他的本性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't know who he is, what he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.18,0:38:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是個危險人物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He is a dangerous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.93,0:38:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再給他點時間  埃米爾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Give him little more time, Emir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.39,0:38:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙可能會證明  他身上有高貴的血統\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Man may prove that has some noble blood in him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.73,0:39:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如坐這裏吧  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How about here, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.95,0:39:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菜單上有很多可選項  但我們推薦雞肉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's an open menu, but we do recommend a chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.13,0:39:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要什麼  林奇先生  菜單上有很多可選項\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What can I get you, Mr. Lynch? It's an open menu,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.30,0:39:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們推薦雞肉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but we do recommend a chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.59,0:39:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要牛排\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll steak.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.07,0:39:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給這位先驅來份牛排\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Steak for the pioneer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.56,0:39:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.81,0:39:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都叫我穆薩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They call me Moussa.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.68,0:39:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我的真名叫巴普蒂斯特  我已經死了200年了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But my name is Baptiste. I'm dead 200 years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.53,0:39:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巫毒大師\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Voodoo poisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.53,0:39:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是無害的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm harmless.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.14,0:39:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都在觀察你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.67,0:40:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等著看你是什麼樣的人  先驅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Waiting to see who you are, pioneer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.92,0:40:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你見過他了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you met him yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.26,0:40:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你見過他了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you met him yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.81,0:40:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是伊甸蘋果最後的守護者  朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We are the last to protect the Apple, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.39,0:40:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一旦做出錯誤的選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pick the wrong choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.48,0:40:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會把我們全部打入無限時空\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you'll send us all to infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.24,0:40:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.87,0:40:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屬於你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.71,0:40:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要帶領他們找到伊甸蘋果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're going to lead them right to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.22,0:40:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我會把蘋果吃掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, I'm going to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.23,0:41:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What the fuck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.60,0:41:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他必須再次進入阿尼姆斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He has to go back in the Animus.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.81,0:41:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.83,0:41:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他需要休息一段時間  才能再次進入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He needs more time before he goes in again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.71,0:41:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們沒時間了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.12,0:41:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.31,0:41:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會拿他的生命冒險\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I won't risk his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.90,0:42:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我只好找其他人代勞了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll have to find someone else to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.19,0:43:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到你了  猛男\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're up, slugger.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.33,0:43:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我瘋了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.54,0:43:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我瘋了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.25,0:43:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘋狂想感覺如此孤寂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Crazy for feeling so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.22,0:43:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們打算把他再次送進阿尼姆斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're getting him back in again.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.21,0:43:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們應該在他背叛我們之前阻止他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We should stop him before he betrays us.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.72,0:43:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,設置好中斷日期\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Set the date for the six.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.35,0:43:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他的情況惡化  就把他拉出來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If his condition deteriorates, pull him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.31,0:43:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你父親說...  -我不管他說過什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You father... - I don't care what my father said.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.97,0:43:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底做錯了什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What in the world did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.48,0:44:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-卡爾  聽我說  -我瘋狂嘗試...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Cal, listen to me. - I'm crazy for trying...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.36,0:44:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說  你必須跟阿圭拉保持合體狀態\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Listen to me. You have to stay with Aguilar.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.07,0:44:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘋狂想哭泣...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Crazy for crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.45,0:44:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脫離同步狀態可能會有危險\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Staying in synch-void could be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.92,0:44:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我瘋狂地愛著你...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I'm crazy for loving you...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.16,0:44:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快他們將進軍格拉納達\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Soon they will march on Granada.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.46,0:45:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,默罕默德蘇丹王很軟弱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sultan Muhammad is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.26,0:45:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他為了救王子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He'll surrender the Apple
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.14,0:45:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會交出蘋果  背叛信條\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and betray the Creed to save the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.93,0:45:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛讓我們軟弱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The love makes us weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.23,0:45:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我願意犧牲自己的親骨肉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gladly I'll sacrifice my flesh and blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.57,0:45:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換取信條永存\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for survival of the Creed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.75,0:45:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今日若死  你無需為我落淚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When I die today, don't waste your tears for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.12,0:46:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主已給出指示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Lord spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.15,0:46:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And he said:
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.07,0:46:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"一個人若不住在我裏面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"If a man abide not in me
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.32,0:46:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就會被丟進火裏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he is cast into the fire
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.45,0:46:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被焚燒殆盡"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and he is burned!"
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.62,0:46:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,數十年以來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For decades,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.96,0:47:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都活在因宗教紛爭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you have lived in the world torn apart
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.58,0:47:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而分崩離析的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}by religious discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.80,0:47:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不久之後  多虧上帝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But soon, thanks to God
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.14,0:47:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和宗教裁判所\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and Inquisition
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.09,0:47:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們將徹底清除這種疾病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we will purge this disease!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.94,0:47:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你們面前的罪人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The sinners before you,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.86,0:47:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,企圖保護格拉納達的異教王子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}sought to defend the heretic prince of Granada,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.94,0:47:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裏是聖戰要攻下的最後一個異教徒據點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the last heathen stronghold in our holy war.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.66,0:47:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So today,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.87,0:47:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在國王和王后的見證下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}before our king and queen
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.33,0:47:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我發誓  我們都將在上帝的聖火中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I swear we shall wash ourselves clean,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.17,0:47:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗淨污穢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in the holy fire of God!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.83,0:47:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Behold...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.51,0:48:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝的旨意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}God's will!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.10,0:48:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你將眼睜睜看著你的師父被燒死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You will watch your mentor burn
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.75,0:48:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後你也將受盡折磨而死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and then you will die the slowest.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.20,0:48:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將榮耀歸於未來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Give glory to the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.13,0:48:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是我們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.66,0:49:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正在同步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He is synchronizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.89,0:49:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死的異教徒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Damned heretics!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.74,0:49:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別讓他們跑了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.54,0:55:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.30,0:55:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除同步完成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Complete desynch.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.76,0:55:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放他下來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.73,0:55:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快叫醫護人員來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Call the medics!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.90,0:55:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事了  卡爾  堅持住  卡爾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay. It's okay. Cal, stay with me. Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.02,0:55:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堅持住  沒事了  快點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stay... It's okay. Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.12,0:56:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事了  看著我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay. Okay. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.85,0:56:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看著我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.24,0:56:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的腿失去知覺了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't feel my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.84,0:56:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體麻痹只是暫時的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Paralysis is temporal.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.33,0:56:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壞消息是什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's the bad news?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.33,0:56:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它引起了神經分裂  但我們把你治好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It caused a neurological split but we got you through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.45,0:56:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一次僥倖而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.59,0:56:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會死在這裏的  對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna die in here, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.55,0:56:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.80,0:57:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你憑借你的自由意志進去  就不會死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not if you go in there on your own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.89,0:57:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.73,0:57:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.73,0:57:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能找到伊甸蘋果的人只剩下你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Apple. You're the only one left who can find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.65,0:57:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們能結束痛苦  卡爾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We can put an end to pain, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.89,0:57:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫助所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.56,0:57:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你從哪裏找到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.51,0:57:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父親在你母親的兇殺現場找到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My father recovered it from the scene of your mother's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.65,0:57:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後帶到這裏來保管\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And brought it here for safekeeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.43,0:57:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保管\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Safekeeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.90,0:58:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這是偷竊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.30,0:58:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你母親的項鏈  我想交給你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's your mother's necklace. I wanted you to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.71,0:58:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他為什麼會去那裏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why was he there?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.23,0:58:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-去救她  -誰要害她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- To save her. - From whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.17,0:58:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-她的同僚  -那跟你有什麼關係\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Her own people. - What's that got to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.75,0:58:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺客和聖殿騎士已經交戰了數個世紀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Assassins and Templars have been at war for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.80,0:58:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望能改變這局面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I aim to change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.81,0:58:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對哦  我忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's right, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.08,0:58:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的目的是根除暴力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're here to combat aggression.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.78,0:58:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜歡你的方式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't think I like your methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.89,0:58:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一個科學家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.27,0:58:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來這裏是為了治好我暴力的一面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm here to be cured of violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.40,0:58:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有誰能治好你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who's gonna cure you?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.49,0:59:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是在餵養一頭野獸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're feeding the beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.66,0:59:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在使他變得愈發強大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're making him stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.92,0:59:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是萊肯博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am Dr Rikkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.97,0:59:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我亞倫吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Alan.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.80,0:59:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我負責管理阿布斯泰戈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I look after things here in Abstergo.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.18,1:00:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不喜歡讓外人插手  對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You like to keep things in the family, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.00,1:00:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.77,1:00:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們給你造成不適  很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry if we caused you any discomfort.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.61,1:00:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼需要我幫忙的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is there anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.94,1:00:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我離開這裏怎麼樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How about you let me out of here?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.50,1:00:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事我辦不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's something I can't manage.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.38,1:00:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來跟你做一筆交易的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm here to make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.09,1:00:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要伊甸蘋果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need the Apple.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.68,1:00:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也需要你幫我們找到它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And we need you to get it for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.56,1:00:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在阿尼姆斯裏一直在解除同步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've been desynching in the Animus.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.52,1:00:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你不要再那樣做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need you not to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.73,1:00:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要把我送進那台機器裏了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sending me back to the machine?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.73,1:00:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你已經讓我們看到我們需要看到的情形了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, you've already shown us what we needed to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.07,1:00:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你會釋放我們嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Will you let us free then?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.25,1:01:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你希望從那個新人身上得到什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you hope to gain from the newcomer?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.34,1:01:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓所有人都受益的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something that'll benefit us all.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.09,1:01:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括你  穆薩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You too, Moussa.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.91,1:01:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對他們做了什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What have you done to them?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.12,1:01:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你用自己的意志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's what happens
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.10,1:01:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進行時空回溯  就會產生這種後果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if you don't enter in regression on your own volition.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.13,1:01:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認識這個嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you recognize this?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.97,1:01:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是刺客之刃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's Assassin's blade.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.14,1:02:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父親正是用這把刀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is the actual one...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.23,1:02:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奪去了你母親的生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}your father used to take your mother's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.28,1:02:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也在這裏  你知道嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's here, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.20,1:02:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個母親的死亡  卡爾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mother's death, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.58,1:02:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠不該讓她兒子看到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not something a boy should ever be made to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.76,1:03:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣做不對\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.76,1:03:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你讓我別無選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You left me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.51,1:03:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定要靠自己的自由意志進去  是你說的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He has to go in on his own free will, you said that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.55,1:03:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我只能去協商  -你是指操縱吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I had to negotiate. - You mean manipulate?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.93,1:03:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向長老們承諾了我們會把伊甸蘋果送到倫敦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I assured the Elders we would have the Apple for London.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.32,1:03:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下兩天時間了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's in two days.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.28,1:03:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不想知道自己的過去  也不想認識自己的父親\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He doesn't want to know his past, or his father.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.83,1:03:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想毀掉這兩樣東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He wants to destroy them, both.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.00,1:03:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不是在製造怪物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're not in the business of creating monsters.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.62,1:03:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們沒有製造它們  也沒有毀掉它們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We neither created them nor destroyed them.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.40,1:03:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不過是將它們拋向自己必然的信念\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We merely abandoned them to their own inexorable faith.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.48,1:04:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你是你母親的孩子  -什麼意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You're your mother's son. - What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.65,1:04:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你體內的血液不屬於你自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Blood that flows through you is not your own.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.03,1:04:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而屬於信條\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Belongs to the Creed.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.70,1:04:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你母親深知這一點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your mother knew that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.79,1:04:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她用死換來信條的傳承\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She died so the Creed may live.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.92,1:04:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我到底是怎麼回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Remind me how, exactly!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.13,1:04:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到的事  是我幹的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What you saw, I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.30,1:04:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你殺了她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You murdered her.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.60,1:04:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我殺了她  總比讓那台機器弄死她要好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I took her life rather than have it stolen by that machine.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.94,1:04:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人因其崇高的使命而成長\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Man grows with the greatness of his task.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.78,1:05:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該把你也殺了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I ought to have killed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.32,1:05:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下不了手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.62,1:05:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.58,1:05:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿著\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.46,1:05:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成你30年前沒能做到的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do what you couldn't do 30 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.00,1:05:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今刺客之刃已在你手中  卡爾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's in your hands now, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.13,1:05:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這正是他們想要的結果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is what they want.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.71,1:05:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Spill my blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.22,1:05:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但千萬不要再進入阿尼姆斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But do not go back in the Animus.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.21,1:05:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.73,1:05:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊甸蘋果當中蘊含著自由意志的基因密碼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Apple contains the genetic code for free will.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.78,1:05:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們會用來毀滅我們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They will use it to destroy us.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.87,1:05:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會找到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna find it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.75,1:05:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後看著他們  毀掉你和你的信條\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And watch them destroy you and your Creed.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.20,1:05:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信條是殺不死的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can not kill the Creed.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.70,1:05:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它根植於你的血液中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's in your blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.08,1:05:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊甸蘋果就是一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Apple is everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.79,1:05:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你母親為了保護它犧牲了生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your mother died to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.13,1:06:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她當年別無選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.97,1:06:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.05,1:07:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要殺了信條\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're gonna kill the Creed!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.94,1:07:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶我去阿尼姆斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take me to the Animus.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.12,1:07:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我放進去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Put me in.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.25,1:07:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備阿尼姆斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Prepare the Animus.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.96,1:07:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自願回溯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Voluntary regression.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.92,1:07:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道殺手的名字是怎麼得來的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you know how the Assassins came to be named?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.26,1:07:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是根據阿拉伯詞語"哈薩辛"演變來的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}From an Arabic word "Hashashin".
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.76,1:07:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們曾是社會的棄徒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They were society's outcasts.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.79,1:07:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們會偷盜  冷血地殺人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Those who stole, who murdered in cold blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.27,1:07:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們都嘲弄他們  叛黨  白癡  癮君子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People ridiculed them... Rebels, fools, drug addicts.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.94,1:07:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其實他們很明智\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But they were wise.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.82,1:07:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們利用這種罵名  來隱藏自身對信條的忠貞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They used this reputation to hide the dedication to principles
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.90,1:07:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至瞞過了最強大的敵人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}beyond those of even their strongest enemies.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.37,1:08:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為此  我很欽佩他們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And for that I admire them.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.96,1:08:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你不是其中的一員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you're not one of those men.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.17,1:08:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.93,1:08:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就試試看吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's find out.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.48,1:08:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始回溯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Commencing regression.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.75,1:08:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我畢生的事業\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is my life's work.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.57,1:08:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.50,1:09:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了信條\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For the Creed.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.24,1:09:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們自身的生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our own lives...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.71,1:09:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是  我們為後世留下什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What matters is what we leave behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.61,1:09:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘇丹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sultan...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.24,1:09:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把伊甸蘋果交出來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Surrender the Apple.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.00,1:10:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些保護你的刺客都已經走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your Assassin protectors are gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.12,1:10:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信條已經完了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Creed is finished.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.16,1:10:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我兒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My son.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.91,1:11:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏面是人類第一次違抗命令的種子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here lies the seed of man's first disobedience,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.79,1:11:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是自由意志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of free will itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.09,1:11:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了伊甸蘋果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks to the Apple of Eden,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.22,1:11:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這已知的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the known world
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.18,1:11:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將會被引入新紀元\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}shall be ushered into a new age.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.69,1:11:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個和平的新紀元\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One of peace,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.40,1:12:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裏  所有彼此敵對的人類\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in which all the warring populations of mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.03,1:12:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將完全服從聖殿的統治\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}shall bow in perfect obedience to our one templar rule.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.06,1:13:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊甸蘋果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Apple.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.81,1:13:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.69,1:13:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.23,1:13:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了信條\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For the Creed.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.36,1:15:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.50,1:16:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原諒我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.60,1:18:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經結束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's over!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.82,1:18:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有刺客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Assassin!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.56,1:18:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信仰之躍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A leap of faith.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.83,1:19:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在在哪兒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.09,1:19:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是個軍事港口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It looks like a military port.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.39,1:19:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位於加的斯  帕洛斯德拉夫龍特拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kadiz, Palos de la Frontera.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.77,1:20:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺客為此而死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Assassins died for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.69,1:20:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你的生命去保護它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Protect it with your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.15,1:20:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是信條的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am a friend of the Creed.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.07,1:20:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶入你的墳墓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take it to your grave.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.33,1:20:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我發誓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I swear.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.18,1:20:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在說什麼  翻譯一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What is it? Translation.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.48,1:20:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追尋著太陽的光芒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Following the light of the sun,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.21,1:21:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我將拋下這個舊世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I shall leave this old world behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.78,1:21:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是克裏斯托弗·哥倫布\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's Christopher Columbus.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.20,1:21:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的墳墓在哪裏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where is he buried?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.78,1:21:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的遺體被轉送回了西班牙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}His remains were returned to Spain.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.40,1:21:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的墳墓在塞維利亞大教堂裏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}His tomb is in Seville Cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.16,1:21:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們找到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.70,1:21:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全明星們  過來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey All Stars, come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.00,1:22:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑一個\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pick one.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.92,1:22:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便選一個\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.35,1:22:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-休息大廳發生襲擊事件  -封鎖阿尼姆斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Breach in common room. - Seal the Animus.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.62,1:22:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是記憶嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is it a memory?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.58,1:22:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.93,1:23:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.90,1:23:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-傳輸裝置如何了  -準備就緒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Transport? - Standing by.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.91,1:23:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護好阿尼姆斯  肅清整個機構\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Protect the Animus. Purge the facility.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.12,1:24:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要先把你救出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I need to get you out of here first.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.34,1:24:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不行  -我們必須走了  索菲婭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No! - We have to leave, Sophia.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.38,1:24:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.93,1:24:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.37,1:25:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是一個人  卡爾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are not alone, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.83,1:25:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你從來都不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You never were.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.85,1:25:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-開門  -快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Open... - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.78,1:26:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都盲目追尋著真相時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where other men blindly follow the truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.59,1:26:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-記住  -一切皆虛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- remember... - Nothing is true.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.71,1:26:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都被道德或法律束縛時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where other men are limited by morality or law,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.05,1:26:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-記住  -無事不允\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- remember... - Everything is permitted.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.84,1:26:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在黑暗中侍奉光明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We work in the darkness to serve the light.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.22,1:26:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是刺客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We are Assassins.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.13,1:26:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在要怎樣  先驅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What now, pioneer?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.68,1:27:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要戰鬥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.70,1:30:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.12,1:31:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,榮譽將屬於你父親\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The glory will go to your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.17,1:31:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們都知道是誰找到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But we both know who found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.05,1:31:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屬於你的光輝時刻會到來的  孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your time will come, my child.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.39,1:31:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,213.21)}{\fn方正宋黑_GBK\fs11\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\fad(1000,900)\c&HC4EFFF&}倫敦  聖殿大廳
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.23,1:32:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們會為此把諾貝爾和平獎頒給你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They'll give you a Nobel peace prize for this.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.99,1:32:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好開始寫演講辭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You better start writing your speech.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.78,1:32:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*-我看過你的演講辭了  -然後呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I've read yours. - And?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.83,1:32:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們剷除了自由意志  就將刺客兄弟會消滅了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If we eradicate free will, we eradicate the Assassins.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.46,1:32:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們就像是荼毒社會長達數個世紀的癌癥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A cancer that has menaced society for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.09,1:32:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是我的最佳作品  但意思都表達清楚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not my best work, but it gets the point across.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.01,1:32:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一直在尋找解決辦法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We've been looking for solutions.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.43,1:32:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你解決了這個問題\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've eliminated the problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.37,1:32:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我的項目...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So my program...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.33,1:33:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次為這個社會帶來了秩序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Has brought order to society for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.42,1:33:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一切都是我的功勞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm accountable for this.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.46,1:33:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經算上你的功勞了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've already been accounted for.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.21,1:33:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的成果都屬於長老會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our work belongs to the Elders.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.42,1:33:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是他們最光榮的時刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is their finest hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.97,1:33:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對我撒謊了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.72,1:33:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've always known
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.68,1:33:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你心裏  科學排第一位  聖殿騎士團排第二\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that in your heart you're a scientist first, templar second.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.98,1:33:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最近的工作實在太令人嘆為觀止了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your recent work has impressed as much
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.02,1:33:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那恰恰證實了我們的信仰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but it has confirmed our belief
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.97,1:33:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是人類是無法獲得救贖的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that mankind cannot be redeemed.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.36,1:33:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你早就盤算好了一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So you've thought of everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.91,1:33:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不算吧  我的演講辭就沒想好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not quite. My speech.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.24,1:33:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能加上你出色的開場白就更好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It could do with one of your elegant openings.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.91,1:33:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我成了死神\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now I've become death,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.04,1:33:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的毀滅者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the destroyer of worlds.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.00,1:33:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太確定我能否讓這一切實現\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not sure that I could make that work.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.02,1:34:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚  我很榮幸地向大家介紹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It is with great pleasure tonight that I introduce
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.49,1:34:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們古老騎士團的未來的構建者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the architect of our ancient order's future.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.41,1:34:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有請阿布斯泰戈基金會的總裁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please welcome the CEO of Abstergo Foundation,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.58,1:34:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞倫·萊肯博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dr. Alan Rikkin.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.35,1:34:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨著伊甸蘋果被重新尋回\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}With the recovery of the Apple,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.68,1:34:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在擁有了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we are now in possession
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.85,1:34:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於人類本能的完整基因地圖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of the complete genetic road map to humanity's instincts.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.11,1:34:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何能導致獨立\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Any impulse towards independence,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.48,1:35:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抗拒或反叛的衝動  都將被清除\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}resistance or rebellion will be crushed.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.95,1:35:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何違背人類進步的體征\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Any predisposition that might oppose our march of progress
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.50,1:35:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在都能被根除\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}can now be eradicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.30,1:35:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只需大喊一聲  你就會沒命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All I have to do is shout.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.47,1:35:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來幫助你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm here to help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.72,1:35:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是來幫助我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you're here to help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.47,1:35:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我幫不了你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't help you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.44,1:35:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼那些偉大的計劃呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about all those great plans?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.48,1:35:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治癒暴力  攻擊性行為\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cure violence, combat aggression.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.86,1:35:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's not going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.91,1:35:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你開啟的這一切  索菲  你不能轉身離開\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've started this, Sophie. You don't get to walk away.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.79,1:35:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都知道接下來會怎樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We both know what happens next.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.84,1:36:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並非所有東西都有資格活著\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not everything deserves to live.
